INFOMap made by Biohazard.pt Hey, so here is my first deathrun map. As you can see I am a very variate mapper. Went from Zombie horde, to surf, to deathrun mapper. This map is quite simple, nice layout. Took me a lot of time because I had lot of problems with compile. Enjoy.
MAP INFOType: Deathrun Players: 60vs4 - Simple layout. - Standart textures. - Two "secrets". - Three ways of killing the Terrorists. - Automatic, semi-automatic and manual traps. - Quite difficult with experient Terrorist. - HDR ligthing. - Variate ambient_generics. - CLASS CHOOSER WHEN ON TERRORIST TEAM**.
TRAP INFOLEVEL 1 1 - Exploding gas leak 2 - Disappearing bridge 3 - Spike jail 4 - Spike ramp 5 - Automatic crusher 6 - Lethal/non-lethal ramps 7 - Tunnel blade 8 - Pushing fan 9 - Exploding barrels 10 - Falling block LEVEL 2 1 - Pool drain to spikes 2 - Lightning hit 3 - Automatic rotating ramps 4 - Freeze to fall 5 - Tricky stairs 6 - Laser pool 7 - Rotating walls (with reverse rotating on click) 8 - Rotating blade 9 - Particle eater 10 - ? 11 - Shocking energy bolt
SCREENSHOT INFOScreenshot 1 - Finish zone Screenshot 2 - Spawn zone Screenshot 3 - Class chooser for Terrorists Screenshot 4 - Level 1 traps Screenshot 5 - Outside spawn zone Screenshot 6 - Level 2 traps
**CLASS CHOOSER INFO- When on Terrorist team, you can either choose to be a fast Terrorist, with enhanced speed, or you can choose to be a Terrorist with a USP. This proves to be useful when you want to avoid getting damage on trap that explode or move faster to never let any CT escape. Enjoy :)
If you want to post this map on other forums go ahead but give me credit for my own map. Thanks go to Unreal, BigBangQuint and Aurora (JJ45). Please feel free to rate, stamp or/and post some feedback.

This is a mix between Deathrun and obstical course, or basicaly a double deathrun where both teams need to do a obstical course and can sabotage the other team after they made it past every obstical.

This map is a AI controlled deathrun map, therefore CT players is NOT needed to control each sets of traps.

There is only terrorist spawnpoints, therefore player can respawn by joining terrorist again upon death.

If you cannot join Terrorist due to limited teams, use rcon or in server console, type in mp_limitteams 20.

For single player: player can use no clip to play each traps without worries about reseting teleporters and waypoints

For multiplayer: one player must be alive in terrorist, if all players die the map restarts. To prevent this from happening, one player should stay back until someone respawn before he attempts any traps. 

Or, try to add a bot to the server, the server will create a nav file and restart the map, then the map will be ready to add a bot, the bot will be on Terrorist and will not move nor attack, preventing map restart.


------------------
Updates:
Increase slot to 32 players.

-=Deathrun_Randomonium=-

This is a deathrun collaboration with 6 stages. The round begins in a spawn. When any player presses the button in the middle of the spawn, a stage gets selected randomly (16.6667% chance stage ''X'' gets selected). That one will be played. The CT's get teleported to the map and the T's get teleported to the trapcontrol area.

Every stage has it's own texture scheme, traps and ending.

From there on, it works like any other deathrun map. The CT's try to avoid the traps and get to the end so they can kill the T's.

Many thanks to the contributors and beta testers.
Also thanks to Bravesurf for making the custom decals in the spawn and to Komaokc for the skybox.

Mappers:

Helix
Silverlol
Komaokc
Ryan S
ParadoXX

Collab leader: WireleZz.

Important:

The map is designed for 66 tick, but can also be played on 100 but with less smoothness. 
Noblock is definetly required to play this map. 
There are 2 Terrorist spawns and 70 Counter-Terrorist spawns. Please disable teambalancing on your server. 

Have fun!

Helix & WireleZz

Video:

The video is old - V1

Firstly, why did I remake this map? Well I believed that this map had a "Excellent Gameplay". You may not agree, but thats what I believe. It had Good GamePlay ( what I believe ) but bad texture, endings and no secrets.

If you played the original version of the map by Jogy, you may wonder "What did this "idiot" do to the eleventh trap (The Hammers Of Doom)", Hehehe I made I made it easier by making each hammer go at a different speed, the first one is at 250, then the second 300 and the last one 350. The default speed in the original map was 350, so thats how I made it easier.

Why did I add MiniStages? Well the name is deathrun_pro right? so it must be tested on skill, Counter Strike Source main skills. I added ministages that you would need to pass while playing in the game, each level has an exit, if you did not know the skill, although you had to sacrifice 30 HP to leave.

What I did to this map is, retexture, redesign and re-edit the traps. I added a new trap only one ( It was a filler ) and secrets. There are 3 Secret Grenades with cool lazors and a secret ending, opened by the colour keypad.

I would like to thank LionHeartnl/Whazaaaaa for making the BHOP Ending, Video, ideas and inspiration. 

Edit:
No more crashing.
Brighter - due to the hole in the ceiling.
--------------------------------------------------
LunarKirby The UnRealistic Mapper
www.SteamGamers.com
